  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_40",
    "english": "Taimanin, student of Gosha Academy. A Fire Art user and a classmate of Shinohara Mari and Nanase Mai.\n\nShe uses her own quick-draw technique, in which she lights her sword aflame in the sheath and unleashes the power of her Fire Art by burning her enemies as she slashes them.\n\nCheerful in the academy, but she hates studying, so she gets help from Shinohara Mari or Nanase Mai. She often acts childish when she wants attention, or gets jealous at people who are better than her.",
    "japanese": "Taimanin, student of Gosha Academy. A Fire Art user and a classmate of Shinohara Mari and Nanase Mai.\n\nShe uses her own quick-draw technique, in which she lights her sword aflame in the sheath and unleashes the power of her Fire Art by burning her enemies as she slashes them.\n\nCheerful in the academy, but she hates studying, so she gets help from Shinohara Mari or Nanase Mai. She often acts childish when she wants attention, or gets jealous at people who are better than her.",
    "korean": "Taimanin, student of Gosha Academy. A Fire Art user and a classmate of Shinohara Mari and Nanase Mai.\n\nShe uses her own quick-draw technique, in which she lights her sword aflame in the sheath and unleashes the power of her Fire Art by burning her enemies as she slashes them.\n\nCheerful in the academy, but she hates studying, so she gets help from Shinohara Mari or Nanase Mai. She often acts childish when she wants attention, or gets jealous at people who are better than her.",
    "chinese_simplified": "Taimanin, student of Gosha Academy. A Fire Art user and a classmate of Shinohara Mari and Nanase Mai.\n\nShe uses her own quick-draw technique, in which she lights her sword aflame in the sheath and unleashes the power of her Fire Art by burning her enemies as she slashes them.\n\nCheerful in the academy, but she hates studying, so she gets help from Shinohara Mari or Nanase Mai. She often acts childish when she wants attention, or gets jealous at people who are better than her.",
    "chinese_traditional": "Taimanin, student of Gosha Academy. A Fire Art user and a classmate of Shinohara Mari and Nanase Mai.\n\nShe uses her own quick-draw technique, in which she lights her sword aflame in the sheath and unleashes the power of her Fire Art by burning her enemies as she slashes them.\n\nCheerful in the academy, but she hates studying, so she gets help from Shinohara Mari or Nanase Mai. She often acts childish when she wants attention, or gets jealous at people who are better than her.",
    "spanish": "Taimanin, student of Gosha Academy. A Fire Art user and a classmate of Shinohara Mari and Nanase Mai.\n\nShe uses her own quick-draw technique, in which she lights her sword aflame in the sheath and unleashes the power of her Fire Art by burning her enemies as she slashes them.\n\nCheerful in the academy, but she hates studying, so she gets help from Shinohara Mari or Nanase Mai. She often acts childish when she wants attention, or gets jealous at people who are better than her."
